com.microsoft.azure.storage.blob

Class StorageURL

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.storage.blob.StorageURL
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlobURL, ContainerURL, ServiceURL

    public abstract class StorageURL
extends Object
    Represents a URL to a Azure storage object. Typically this class is only needed to generate a new pipeline. In most cases, one of the other URL types will be more useful.

        Parameters:

        name - The name to be appended.

        Throws:
